{"tid":184730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[估地方]洋男嘿咻OL後急返鄉　遭控性侵無法離境","createTime":"2017-04-03T04:19:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-03T16:45:05.000Z","uid":54733,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5c89afc8e129bd46cc3f97c2dc92f0d1915e6458","tid":184730,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T04:19:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">洋男嘿咻OL後急返鄉　遭控性侵無法離境</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170403/640_5a8efc76a4a9eaa1625584bb13ec77fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170403%2F640_5a8efc76a4a9eaa1625584bb13ec77fc.jpg&h=a0ff471a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n法國籍男子羅賓來台考察，與25歲OL發生性關係，羅賓上月簽證到期要返國，<span style=\"color: red;\">OL認為他是「人到手後就想落跑」，告羅賓性侵</span>。<br />\n<br />\n今日出版的《自由時報》報導，警方調查，36歲羅賓今年1月來台考察，租住北市康定路某大樓，日前透過臉書認識想學法文的OL，兩人約見面交流法文、看電影，後來羅賓帶她回住處發生性關係。上月羅賓簽證到期，<span style=\"color: red;\">告知OL回國一段時間再來台，OL認為羅賓想拋棄她，控告羅賓對她性侵</span>；羅賓承認與OL交往，堅稱兩情相悅。<br />\n<br />\n檢察官為查明事實，無法讓他馬上離境，須將全案釐清後，確認羅賓未涉案才會放行，讓他十分無奈。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"51b8507fd950e2c7a07ba1d7bd1ae517ec25bfcd","tid":184730,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T04:20:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/hot/20170403/1090046\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fhot%2F20170403%2F1090046&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtb9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=19e0f889\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/hot/20170403/1090046</a>"},{"pid":"1613ae814b3e468e257d384313d589a3211617a4","tid":184730,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T04:21:53.000Z","msg":"高級既法國洋腸<br />\n別讓他跑了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c51f83cb81b2a6aa8b1370213f51f149e0935a5","tid":184730,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited